.SH DESCRIPTION
Agentusage is a small utility to set up Claude Code slash commands
(\fI\,/save\/\fP and \fI\,/load\/\fP) for persisting session transcripts across projects
in a single repository.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
\fB\-s\fR, \fB\-\-setup\fR <dir>
set up agentusage with given git\-managed store dir,
where it will store agent transcripts. This should
be a dedicated repository, not a project code repo.
.TP
\fB\-h\fR, \fB\-\-help\fR
display this help and exit
.TP
\fB\-v\fR, \fB\-\-version\fR
output version information and exit
